{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I am going to speak about corruption,"},{"time":2000,"text":"but I would like to juxtapose"},{"time":5000,"text":"two different things."},{"time":7000,"text":"One is the large global economy,"},{"time":12000,"text":"the large globalized economy,"},{"time":15000,"text":"and the other one is the small, and very limited,"},{"time":18000,"text":"capacity of our traditional governments"},{"time":22000,"text":"and their international institutions"},{"time":24000,"text":"to govern, to shape, this economy."},{"time":28000,"text":"Because there is this asymmetry,"},{"time":33000,"text":"which creates, basically,"},{"time":36000,"text":"failing governance."},{"time":38000,"text":"Failing governance in many areas:"},{"time":40000,"text":"in the area of corruption and the area of destruction of the environment,"},{"time":44000,"text":"in the area of exploitation of women and children,"},{"time":47000,"text":"in the area of climate change,"},{"time":51000,"text":"in all the areas in which we really need"},{"time":54000,"text":"a capacity to reintroduce"},{"time":59000,"text":"the primacy of politics"},{"time":62000,"text":"into the economy,"},{"time":64000,"text":"which is operating in a worldwide arena."},{"time":69000,"text":"And I think corruption,"},{"time":71000,"text":"and the fight against corruption,"},{"time":73000,"text":"and the impact of corruption,"},{"time":75000,"text":"is probably one of the most interesting ways"},{"time":77000,"text":"to illustrate what I mean"},{"time":79000,"text":"with this failure of governance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":82000,"text":"Let me talk about my own experience."},{"time":86000,"text":"I used to work as the director"},{"time":89000,"text":"of the World Bank office in Nairobi"},{"time":92000,"text":"for East Africa."},{"time":94000,"text":"At that time, I noticed"},{"time":96000,"text":"that corruption, that grand corruption,"},{"time":99000,"text":"that systematic corruption,"},{"time":101000,"text":"was undermining everything we were trying to do."},{"time":105000,"text":"And therefore, I began"},{"time":107000,"text":"to not only try to protect"},{"time":110000,"text":"the work of the World Bank,"},{"time":112000,"text":"our own projects, our own programs"},{"time":114000,"text":"against corruption,"},{"time":116000,"text":"but in general, I thought, \"We need a system"},{"time":119000,"text":"to protect the people"},{"time":121000,"text":"in this part of the world"},{"time":123000,"text":"from the ravages of corruption.\""},{"time":126000,"text":"And as soon as I started this work,"},{"time":129000,"text":"I received a memorandum from the World Bank,"},{"time":132000,"text":"from the legal department first,"},{"time":134000,"text":"in which they said, \"You are not allowed to do this."},{"time":136000,"text":"You are meddling in the internal affairs of our partner countries."},{"time":140000,"text":"This is forbidden by the charter of the World Bank,"},{"time":143000,"text":"so I want you to stop your doings.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":146000,"text":"In the meantime, I was chairing"},{"time":148000,"text":"donor meetings, for instance,"},{"time":150000,"text":"in which the various donors,"},{"time":152000,"text":"and many of them like to be in Nairobi --"},{"time":155000,"text":"it is true, it is one of the"},{"time":157000,"text":"unsafest cities of the world,"},{"time":159000,"text":"but they like to be there because the other cities"},{"time":161000,"text":"are even less comfortable."},{"time":164000,"text":"And in these donor meetings, I noticed"},{"time":166000,"text":"that many of the worst projects --"},{"time":168000,"text":"which were put forward"},{"time":170000,"text":"by our clients, by the governments,"},{"time":172000,"text":"by promoters,"},{"time":174000,"text":"many of them representing"},{"time":176000,"text":"suppliers from the North --"},{"time":178000,"text":"that the worst projects"},{"time":180000,"text":"were realized first."},{"time":182000,"text":"Let me give you an example:"},{"time":184000,"text":"a huge power project,"},{"time":186000,"text":"300 million dollars,"},{"time":189000,"text":"to be built smack into"},{"time":191000,"text":"one of the most vulnerable, and one of the most beautiful,"},{"time":194000,"text":"areas of western Kenya."},{"time":197000,"text":"And we all noticed immediately"},{"time":199000,"text":"that this project had no economic benefits:"},{"time":202000,"text":"It had no clients, nobody would buy the electricity there,"},{"time":206000,"text":"nobody was interested in irrigation projects."},{"time":208000,"text":"To the contrary, we knew that this project"},{"time":211000,"text":"would destroy the environment:"},{"time":213000,"text":"It would destroy riparian forests,"},{"time":215000,"text":"which were the basis for"},{"time":217000,"text":"the survival of nomadic groups,"},{"time":219000,"text":"the Samburu and the Turkana in this area."},{"time":223000,"text":"So everybody knew this is a, not a useless project,"},{"time":226000,"text":"this is an absolute damaging, a terrible project --"},{"time":229000,"text":"not to speak about the future indebtedness of the country"},{"time":233000,"text":"for these hundreds of millions of dollars,"},{"time":235000,"text":"and the siphoning off"},{"time":238000,"text":"of the scarce resources of the economy"},{"time":240000,"text":"from much more important activities"},{"time":243000,"text":"like schools, like hospitals and so on."},{"time":245000,"text":"And yet, we all rejected this project,"},{"time":248000,"text":"none of the donors was willing"},{"time":250000,"text":"to have their name connected with it,"},{"time":253000,"text":"and it was the first project to be implemented."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255000,"text":"The good projects, which we as a donor community"},{"time":258000,"text":"would take under our wings,"},{"time":260000,"text":"they took years, you know,"},{"time":262000,"text":"you had too many studies,"},{"time":264000,"text":"and very often they didn't succeed."},{"time":266000,"text":"But these bad projects,"},{"time":268000,"text":"which were absolutely damaging -- for the economy"},{"time":270000,"text":"for many generations, for the environment,"},{"time":273000,"text":"for thousands of families who had to be resettled --"},{"time":276000,"text":"they were suddenly put together"},{"time":278000,"text":"by consortia of banks,"},{"time":281000,"text":"of supplier agencies,"},{"time":283000,"text":"of insurance agencies --"},{"time":285000,"text":"like in Germany, Hermes, and so on --"},{"time":288000,"text":"and they came back very, very quickly,"},{"time":290000,"text":"driven by an unholy alliance"},{"time":292000,"text":"between the powerful elites"},{"time":296000,"text":"in the countries there"},{"time":298000,"text":"and the suppliers from the North."},{"time":300000,"text":"Now, these suppliers"},{"time":302000,"text":"were our big companies."},{"time":304000,"text":"They were the actors of this global market,"},{"time":307000,"text":"which I mentioned in the beginning."},{"time":309000,"text":"They were the Siemenses of this world,"},{"time":312000,"text":"coming from France, from the UK, from Japan,"},{"time":314000,"text":"from Canada, from Germany,"},{"time":316000,"text":"and they were systematically driven"},{"time":319000,"text":"by systematic, large-scale corruption."},{"time":322000,"text":"We are not talking about"},{"time":324000,"text":"50,000 dollars here,"},{"time":326000,"text":"or 100,000 dollars there, or one million dollars there."},{"time":329000,"text":"No, we are talking about 10 million, 20 million dollars"},{"time":332000,"text":"on the Swiss bank accounts,"},{"time":334000,"text":"on the bank accounts of Liechtenstein,"},{"time":336000,"text":"of the president's ministers,"},{"time":340000,"text":"the high officials in the para-statal sectors."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343000,"text":"This was the reality which I saw,"},{"time":345000,"text":"and not only one project like that:"},{"time":347000,"text":"I saw, I would say,"},{"time":349000,"text":"over the years I worked in Africa,"},{"time":351000,"text":"I saw hundreds of projects like this."},{"time":353000,"text":"And so, I became convinced"},{"time":356000,"text":"that it is this systematic corruption"},{"time":359000,"text":"which is perverting economic policy-making in these countries,"},{"time":362000,"text":"which is the main reason"},{"time":365000,"text":"for the misery, for the poverty,"},{"time":368000,"text":"for the conflicts, for the violence,"},{"time":370000,"text":"for the desperation"},{"time":372000,"text":"in many of these countries."},{"time":374000,"text":"That we have today"},{"time":376000,"text":"more than a billion people below the absolute poverty line,"},{"time":379000,"text":"that we have more than a billion people"},{"time":382000,"text":"without proper drinking water in the world,"},{"time":384000,"text":"twice that number,"},{"time":386000,"text":"more than two billion people"},{"time":388000,"text":"without sanitation and so on,"},{"time":390000,"text":"and the consequent illnesses"},{"time":392000,"text":"of mothers and children,"},{"time":395000,"text":"still, child mortality of more than"},{"time":398000,"text":"10 million people every year,"},{"time":400000,"text":"children dying before they are five years old:"},{"time":402000,"text":"The cause of this is, to a large extent,"},{"time":405000,"text":"grand corruption."}]},{"cues":[{"time":407000,"text":"Now, why did the World Bank"},{"time":410000,"text":"not let me do this work?"},{"time":413000,"text":"I found out afterwards,"},{"time":416000,"text":"after I left, under a big fight, the World Bank."},{"time":419000,"text":"The reason was that the members of the World Bank"},{"time":422000,"text":"thought that foreign bribery was okay,"},{"time":425000,"text":"including Germany."},{"time":427000,"text":"In Germany, foreign bribery was allowed."},{"time":429000,"text":"It was even tax-deductible."},{"time":432000,"text":"No wonder that most of the most important"},{"time":434000,"text":"international operators in Germany,"},{"time":437000,"text":"but also in France and the UK"},{"time":439000,"text":"and Scandinavia, everywhere, systematically bribed."},{"time":441000,"text":"Not all of them, but most of them."},{"time":444000,"text":"And this is the phenomenon"},{"time":446000,"text":"which I call failing governance,"},{"time":449000,"text":"because when I then came to Germany"},{"time":451000,"text":"and started this little NGO"},{"time":453000,"text":"here in Berlin, at the Villa Borsig,"},{"time":457000,"text":"we were told, \"You cannot stop"},{"time":460000,"text":"our German exporters from bribing,"},{"time":462000,"text":"because we will lose our contracts."},{"time":465000,"text":"We will lose to the French,"},{"time":467000,"text":"we will lose to the Swedes, we'll lose to the Japanese.\""},{"time":470000,"text":"And therefore, there was a indeed a prisoner's dilemma,"},{"time":473000,"text":"which made it very difficult"},{"time":475000,"text":"for an individual company,"},{"time":477000,"text":"an individual exporting country"},{"time":480000,"text":"to say, \"We are not going to"},{"time":482000,"text":"continue this deadly, disastrous"},{"time":485000,"text":"habit of large companies to bribe.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":489000,"text":"So this is what I mean"},{"time":491000,"text":"with a failing governance structure,"},{"time":494000,"text":"because even the powerful government,"},{"time":496000,"text":"which we have in Germany, comparatively,"},{"time":499000,"text":"was not able to say,"},{"time":501000,"text":"\"We will not allow our companies to bribe abroad.\""},{"time":504000,"text":"They needed help,"},{"time":506000,"text":"and the large companies themselves"},{"time":508000,"text":"have this dilemma."},{"time":510000,"text":"Many of them didn't want to bribe."},{"time":512000,"text":"Many of the German companies, for instance,"},{"time":514000,"text":"believe that they are really"},{"time":516000,"text":"producing a high-quality product"},{"time":518000,"text":"at a good price, so they are very competitive."},{"time":521000,"text":"They are not as good at bribing"},{"time":524000,"text":"as many of their international competitors are,"},{"time":526000,"text":"but they were not allowed"},{"time":528000,"text":"to show their strengths,"},{"time":530000,"text":"because the world was eaten up"},{"time":533000,"text":"by grand corruption."}]},{"cues":[{"time":535000,"text":"And this is why I'm telling you this:"},{"time":539000,"text":"Civil society rose to the occasion."},{"time":543000,"text":"We had this small NGO,"},{"time":545000,"text":"Transparency International."},{"time":547000,"text":"They began to think of"},{"time":549000,"text":"an escape route from this prisoner's dilemma,"},{"time":552000,"text":"and we developed concepts"},{"time":556000,"text":"of collective action,"},{"time":558000,"text":"basically trying to bring various competitors"},{"time":560000,"text":"together around the table,"},{"time":562000,"text":"explaining to all of them"},{"time":564000,"text":"how much it would be in their interests"},{"time":566000,"text":"if they simultaneously would stop bribing,"},{"time":568000,"text":"and to make a long story short,"},{"time":571000,"text":"we managed to eventually"},{"time":573000,"text":"get Germany to sign"},{"time":575000,"text":"together with the other OECD countries"},{"time":577000,"text":"and a few other exporters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":579000,"text":"In 1997, a convention,"},{"time":582000,"text":"under the auspices of the OECD,"},{"time":584000,"text":"which obliged everybody"},{"time":586000,"text":"to change their laws"},{"time":588000,"text":"and criminalize foreign bribery."},{"time":590000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":594000,"text":"Well, thank you. I mean, it's interesting,"},{"time":596000,"text":"in doing this,"},{"time":598000,"text":"we had to sit together with the companies."},{"time":601000,"text":"We had here in Berlin, at the Aspen Institute on the Wannsee,"},{"time":604000,"text":"we had sessions with about"},{"time":606000,"text":"20 captains of industry,"},{"time":608000,"text":"and we discussed with them"},{"time":610000,"text":"what to do about international bribery."},{"time":612000,"text":"In the first session -- we had three sessions"},{"time":614000,"text":"over the course of two years."},{"time":616000,"text":"And President von Weizs√§cker, by the way,"},{"time":619000,"text":"chaired one of the sessions, the first one,"},{"time":621000,"text":"to take the fear away"},{"time":623000,"text":"from the entrepreneurs,"},{"time":626000,"text":"who were not used to deal"},{"time":628000,"text":"with non-governmental organizations."},{"time":630000,"text":"And in the first session, they all said,"},{"time":633000,"text":"\"This is not bribery, what we are doing.\" This is customary there."},{"time":636000,"text":"This is what these other cultures demand."},{"time":639000,"text":"They even applaud it."},{"time":641000,"text":"In fact, [unclear]"},{"time":643000,"text":"still says this today."},{"time":645000,"text":"And so there are still a lot of people"},{"time":647000,"text":"who are not convinced that you have to stop bribing."},{"time":650000,"text":"But in the second session,"},{"time":652000,"text":"they admitted already that they would never do this,"},{"time":654000,"text":"what they are doing in these other countries,"},{"time":657000,"text":"here in Germany, or in the U.K., and so on."},{"time":659000,"text":"Cabinet ministers would admit this."},{"time":662000,"text":"And in the final session, at the Aspen Institute,"},{"time":665000,"text":"we had them all sign an open letter"},{"time":668000,"text":"to the Kohl government, at the time,"},{"time":670000,"text":"requesting that they"},{"time":672000,"text":"participate in the OECD convention."}]},{"cues":[{"time":674000,"text":"And this is, in my opinion,"},{"time":677000,"text":"an example of soft power,"},{"time":679000,"text":"because we were able to convince them"},{"time":681000,"text":"that they had to go with us."},{"time":683000,"text":"We had a longer-term time perspective."},{"time":686000,"text":"We had a broader,"},{"time":688000,"text":"geographically much wider,"},{"time":690000,"text":"constituency we were trying to defend."},{"time":692000,"text":"And that's why the law has changed."},{"time":694000,"text":"That's why Siemens is now in the trouble they are in"},{"time":697000,"text":"and that's why MIN is in the trouble they are in."},{"time":700000,"text":"In some other countries, the OECD convention"},{"time":703000,"text":"is not yet properly enforced."},{"time":705000,"text":"And, again, civil societies"},{"time":707000,"text":"breathing down the neck of the establishment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":710000,"text":"In London, for instance,"},{"time":712000,"text":"where the BAE got away"},{"time":714000,"text":"with a huge corruption case,"},{"time":716000,"text":"which the Serious Fraud Office tried to prosecute,"},{"time":720000,"text":"100 million British pounds,"},{"time":722000,"text":"every year for ten years,"},{"time":724000,"text":"to one particular official of one particular friendly country,"},{"time":727000,"text":"who then bought for"},{"time":729000,"text":"44 billion pounds of military equipment."},{"time":733000,"text":"This case, they are not prosecuting in the UK."},{"time":735000,"text":"Why? Because they consider this"},{"time":737000,"text":"as contrary to the security interest"},{"time":740000,"text":"of the people of Great Britain."},{"time":742000,"text":"Civil society is pushing, civil society"},{"time":744000,"text":"is trying to get a solution to this problem,"},{"time":747000,"text":"also in the U.K.,"},{"time":749000,"text":"and also in Japan, which is not properly enforcing,"},{"time":751000,"text":"and so on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":753000,"text":"In Germany, we are pushing"},{"time":755000,"text":"the ratification of the UN convention,"},{"time":757000,"text":"which is a subsequent convention."},{"time":759000,"text":"We are, Germany, is not ratifying."},{"time":761000,"text":"Why? Because it would make it necessary"},{"time":764000,"text":"to criminalize the corruption"},{"time":767000,"text":"of deputies."},{"time":769000,"text":"In Germany, we have a system where"},{"time":771000,"text":"you are not allowed to bribe a civil servant,"},{"time":774000,"text":"but you are allowed to bribe a deputy."},{"time":777000,"text":"This is, under German law, allowed,"},{"time":780000,"text":"and the members of our parliament don't want to change this,"},{"time":782000,"text":"and this is why they can't sign"},{"time":784000,"text":"the U.N. convention against foreign bribery --"},{"time":787000,"text":"one of they very, very few countries"},{"time":789000,"text":"which is preaching honesty and good governance everywhere in the world,"},{"time":792000,"text":"but not able to ratify the convention,"},{"time":794000,"text":"which we managed to get on the books"},{"time":797000,"text":"with about 160 countries all over the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":800000,"text":"I see my time is ticking."},{"time":802000,"text":"Let me just try to"},{"time":804000,"text":"draw some conclusions from what has happened."},{"time":807000,"text":"I believe that what we managed to achieve"},{"time":811000,"text":"in fighting corruption,"},{"time":814000,"text":"one can also achieve"},{"time":816000,"text":"in other areas of failing governance."},{"time":818000,"text":"By now, the United Nations"},{"time":820000,"text":"is totally on our side."},{"time":822000,"text":"The World Bank has turned from Saulus to Paulus; under Wolfensohn,"},{"time":826000,"text":"they became, I would say, the strongest"},{"time":829000,"text":"anti-corruption agency in the world."},{"time":831000,"text":"Most of the large companies"},{"time":833000,"text":"are now totally convinced"},{"time":835000,"text":"that they have to put in place"},{"time":837000,"text":"very strong policies"},{"time":839000,"text":"against bribery and so on."},{"time":841000,"text":"And this is possible because civil society"},{"time":844000,"text":"joined the companies"},{"time":846000,"text":"and joined the government"},{"time":848000,"text":"in the analysis of the problem,"},{"time":850000,"text":"in the development of remedies,"},{"time":852000,"text":"in the implementation of reforms,"},{"time":855000,"text":"and then later, in the monitoring of reforms."}]},{"cues":[{"time":858000,"text":"Of course, if civil society organizations"},{"time":861000,"text":"want to play that role,"},{"time":863000,"text":"they have to grow into this responsibility."},{"time":867000,"text":"Not all civil society organizations are good."},{"time":870000,"text":"The Ku Klux Klan is an NGO."},{"time":873000,"text":"So, we must be aware"},{"time":875000,"text":"that civil society"},{"time":877000,"text":"has to shape up itself."},{"time":879000,"text":"They have to have a much more"},{"time":881000,"text":"transparent financial governance."},{"time":883000,"text":"They have to have a much more participatory governance"},{"time":886000,"text":"in many civil society organizations."},{"time":889000,"text":"We also need much more competence of civil society leaders."},{"time":892000,"text":"This is why we have set up the governance school"},{"time":895000,"text":"and the Center for Civil Society here in Berlin,"},{"time":897000,"text":"because we believe most of our educational"},{"time":900000,"text":"and research institutions in Germany"},{"time":902000,"text":"and continental Europe in general,"},{"time":904000,"text":"do not focus enough, yet,"},{"time":906000,"text":"on empowering civil society"},{"time":908000,"text":"and training the leadership of civil society."}]},{"cues":[{"time":911000,"text":"But what I'm saying from my very practical experience:"},{"time":914000,"text":"If civil society does it right"},{"time":917000,"text":"and joins the other actors --"},{"time":920000,"text":"in particular, governments,"},{"time":922000,"text":"governments and their international institutions,"},{"time":925000,"text":"but also large international actors,"},{"time":928000,"text":"in particular those which have committed themselves"},{"time":930000,"text":"to corporate social responsibility --"},{"time":932000,"text":"then in this magical triangle"},{"time":935000,"text":"between civil society,"},{"time":937000,"text":"government and private sector,"},{"time":939000,"text":"there is a tremendous chance"},{"time":941000,"text":"for all of us to create a better world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":945000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":947000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}